== Network Information Base System

This is a Open Source System to Monitor Configure and Manage Systems in a new way.It should not be another Monitoring System in your Toolbox. It should be a tool to Integrate other Open Source Projects.  

Actually there are only a Ruby Webinterface based on Ruby ond Rails and Admin-LTE. As Importer for Data the Logstash Projekt ist used and as a Datastorage I hope elasticsearch will do the heavy work.

Things you may want to cover:

* Ruby version: 2.0

* System dependencies: Tested Install on Ubuntu 14.04

* Configuration

* Database creation

* Database initialization

* How to run the test suite

* Services (job queues, cache servers, search engines, etc.)

* Deployment instructions

* ...


Please feel free to use a different markup language if you do not plan to run
<tt>rake doc:app</tt>.
